	Clooney cops    
	 London, June 15 (PTI): Actor George Clooney was out enjoying the picturesque sights of Laglio town in Italy on his bike when he was stopped by two policemen .      
	It turned out that they were just seeking an autograph.       
	The actor obliged them with autographs and also posed for photographs with the policemen with a camera usually used to snap suspects, reports the Daily Mail. The 48-year-old actor is currently on his annual summer holiday to the region, where he owns a lakeside villa.     
	David girl    
	 London (PTI): Soccer star David Beckham wants to have another baby with wife Victoria as he wants his three sons to have a sister. Beckham and his fashionista wife Victoria have three young sons, Brooklyn, 10, Romeo, six and Cruz, four. The football star now wants a baby girl. I really want more kids and I hope it happens soon. I want a little girl. That would be amazing, Beckham said.    
	Sexy Diaz    
	 Los Angeles (PTI): Actress Cameron Diaz, who is known for her slender frame, feels that women should channel their inner sexuality irrespective of their bodies. The blonde bombshell who recently revealed that she is a commitment phobe said that women need not be intimidated by the popular notions of attractiveness, reports Us magazine. Its part of being an animal, its part of being human. 
                                                                                                                                                                 
